import React from 'react'
import {MidFooterWrapper, MidFooterItemWrapper, MidFooterImage, MidFooterTextMain, MidFooterTextSecondary} from './MidFooterElements'

function MidFooter() {
    return (
        <MidFooterWrapper>
            <MidFooterItemWrapper>
                <MidFooterImage>
                    <MidFooterTextMain>70+ </MidFooterTextMain>
                    <MidFooterTextSecondary>Happy Customers</MidFooterTextSecondary>
                    
                </MidFooterImage>
            </MidFooterItemWrapper>
            
        </MidFooterWrapper>
    )
}

export default MidFooter
